{
  "stem": "4710.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then that we saw that-- Jews of Budapest, which were really a substantial part of the Jewish community in Budapest, at that time must have lived possibly-- the records will say it otherwise.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I just-- between 200,000 or 300,000 Jewish people lived in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "A lot of refugees all accumulated there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But no transports arrived from there to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That they are there, still in Budapest, and which is a good thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because gradually, we realized that where we are.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were taken a camp which was called [GERMAN], gypsy camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the original inhabitants were the gypsies there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In fact, one side of the camp, there were still some gypsies there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after about two weeks of being there we arrived, the gypsies were all rounded up and taken to the gas chambers, those gypsies who were in the camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then it dawned on us that there are gas chambers, where they are gassing people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because some people-- you see, one hears from the other that there gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you don't want to believe it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some people, I think, always ask the older inhabitants of the camps, when can we see our parents, or something, who arrived.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They say, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You will have given an opportunity later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it was all lies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, there was no-- by that time, there was-- those who didn't come into the camps, they were-- they were killed on the same day as they arrived.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when the gypsy camp was evacuated, and they were screaming at the night, and we heard it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there was thrown belongings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They had their blankets.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was all on the-- we realized that they were taken to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
